  "keyFeatures": [
    "Highly optimized neural network inference for ARM, x86, WebAssembly, and RISC-V",
    "Multi-platform SIMD acceleration (NEON, AVX512, WebAssembly SIMD, HVX)",
    "Subgraph-based API for defining and running full neural network models",
    "Support for FP32, FP16, BF16, INT8 (QS8/QU8), and 4-bit quantized inference",
    "Sparse inference and memory-optimized runtime execution",
    "Multi-threaded inference via pthreadpool",
    "Indirect convolution algorithm for cache-efficient computation",
    "30+ neural network operators including convolution, pooling, elementwise, and matrix multiply",
    "Used by TensorFlow Lite, PyTorch Mobile, ONNX Runtime, MediaPipe, and TensorFlow.js"
  ],
